==English==

===Adjective===
'''redivivus'''
# Living again; brought back to life
# Having come back to life

===Synonyms===
 [[revived]]
 [[restored]]

===Usage Note===
Redivivus is used postpositively such that it appears after the noun it modifies

===Examples===

His father is a true Hulk Hogan redivivus, last time I went over there he ripped his freakin' shirt off.